                Victorio Cassiano <expan><abbr>vet</abbr><ex>erano</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> VII <lb n="2"/>qui vixit <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> LV Victorii Cle<lb break="no" n="3"/>mentinus et Victorinus et Se<lb break="no" n="4"/>necionius Iulianus filii eius per <lb n="5"/>Victorium Hermetem libertum <lb n="6"/>eius patri piissimo <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>aciendum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uraverunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Sarkophagkasten. Position der Zeilenfälle unsicher.</p>
